{"tid":902581,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"（升值！！！）連環冧價！嘉湖山莊三房戶跌穿500萬","createTime":"2018-11-15T02:26:27.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-15T12:59:42.000Z","uid":147097,"like":13,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"63dff2de079d2ff36517e043b4b38df8d31329c8","tid":902581,"uid":147097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-15T02:26:27.000Z","msg":"「上車樂園」天水圍嘉湖山莊兩房單位連環跌至440萬元低位，其三房戶樓價都跌破「5球」。 <br />\n<br />\n祥益謝利官稱，屋苑樂湖居13座低C室，實用面積548方呎，三房間隔，8月初叫價600萬元，前晚(13日)突然降價至490萬元，即引來多組準買家積極還價。 <br />\n<br />\n事實上，同面積單位，10月成交價仍達約550萬至570萬元，投資者知道機不可失，只叫代理隔空影相睇樓，在別人仍考慮之際，已出價購入，最後成交價僅483.8萬元，<span style=\"color: red;\">呎價約8,828元。</span> <br />\n<br />\n而嘉湖山莊向為上車市場指標，<span style=\"color: red;\">早前三房一套單位呎價跌至約8,400元</span>，再錄呎價低於9,000元買賣。 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n尺價升左<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3fa1e15b84f8d8aa6e5051fbaea23e3d77b7dcb0","tid":902581,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-15T02:28:21.000Z","msg":"兩房會再受壓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e48c43e06a8a67870f0d64cc8a49a7e89b3c9b7e","tid":902581,"uid":147097,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-15T02:28:54.000Z","msg":"其實住保升好 定 天水圍好d<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n嘉湖起碼大d<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"266e7a5a6421b513c095fac9a849e928f6c68345","tid":902581,"uid":57005,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-15T02:31:22.000Z","msg":"覺得咁抵都要還6.2萬價<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nBTW，3房見4字，2房應該3字？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ed8acc19d3db458d39ee904792efbdc15178d00","tid":902581,"uid":32588,"like"